First Department,

May, 1958 *

(May 27, 1958) In the Matter of Reuben Hecht, Petitioner, against Francis W. H. Adams, as Police Commissioner of the City of New York, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss the proceeding is hereby granted, with $10 costs. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin, M. M. Frank and McNally, JJ.
